article.headline: Mitchell-Day scores 22 as Dartmouth takes down Brown 75-71
article.description: — Brandon Mitchell-Day's 22 points helped Dartmouth defeat Brown 75-71 on Saturday.
article.linkText: Mitchell-Day scores 22 as Dartmouth takes down Brown 75-71
article.story: HANOVER, N.H. -- — Brandon Mitchell-Day's 22 points helped Dartmouth defeat Brown 75-71 on Saturday. Mitchell-Day added 10 rebounds for the Big Green (5-12, 1/3 Ivy League). Dusan Neskovic shot 7 for 12 (3 for 5 from 3-point range) and 3 of 4 from the free throw line to add 20 points. Jackson Munro went 3 of 4 from the field to finish with nine points. The Big Green ended a five-game skid with the victory. The Bears (5-14, 1-3) were led in scoring by Nana Owusu-Anane, who finished with 20 points, nine rebounds and two steals. Kino Lilly Jr. added 14 points for Brown. Malachi Ndur also recorded 14 points and three blocks. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
